{"product_id": "15100", "page": 3, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2018-02-10", "text": "5/10\n- Extremely repetitive. You have to basically do the same exact thing over and over again.\n- Extremely buggy. At the beginning, I was okay with the bugs (leaps of faith not working, enemies floating, etc.) but it came to a point where I couldn't finish missions because the game would enter a loop in which the mission would reset itself even after completion or me being teleported inside a mountain because of an enemy hitting me.\n- Parkour: fun but gets boring after a while.\n- Kudos for the story", "hours": 31.1, "username": "kata", "products": 57, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
