{"product_id": "15100", "page": 14, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-23", "text": "The Assassin's Creed is a well known name that I'm sure you heard it.\n- thrilling actions\n- genuine re-creation of the medivial cities\n- beautifully mixing original plot into history\n- critical thinking\nIt's more than an action game. Alta\u00efr didn't just pick up missions and perform bad\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665moves. He questioned.", "hours": 20.8, "user_id": "76561198070282362", "username": "Sgazer", "products": 54, "early_access": false}
