{"product_id": "15100", "page": 15, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-11-18", "text": "TBH it's a pretty bad game. Very repetitive gameplay and controls that just get boring after the first 2 hours or so. The AI in this game are \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 with annoying voices. On top of that, there are certain times where you just have no \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing clue where to go, like the map just does not \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing show you and you just run around like a \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing idiot. The map shows you all these garbage uncessary symbols that just cluster the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing map. \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 this game.", "hours": 8.4, "user_id": "76561198045291530", "username": "denka", "products": 60, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
