{"product_id": "15100", "page": 22, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-10-05", "text": "I haven't played such a repetitive game in a long time. After a while it gets really boring. I would normally skip this game and go straight to sequel, but then I would miss storyline, which is basically the only drive why even play this game. I'm still surprised how I managed to finish this game. Also about gameplay, I really hate that I didn't feel like assassin at all. Stealth is unnecessary, since you can fight off unlimited amount of soldiers and it's way quicker.", "hours": 30.7, "user_id": "76561198031387862", "username": "[-Toka-]", "products": 108, "early_access": false}
