{"product_id": "15100", "page": 38, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-05-14", "text": "I bought and beat this game on xbox. Loved it. Bought this again on pc with a bundle. Bundle was cheaper then buying the rest. So I am playing it again on pc. It has more stuff to do but not much. Check for a desync of your graphics which cause a glitch in leaps of faith. Otherwise. Good port. It is easy to fix with your graphics options.", "hours": 7.8, "username": "ali-sama", "products": 1254, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
