{"product_id": "15100", "page": 40, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-04-17", "text": "While a bit glitchy at times, definitely enjoyed experiencing the game that started a (perhaps played out and) successful franchise.", "hours": 30.5, "user_id": "76561198067803453", "username": "Ruh Roh Rhaggy", "products": 25, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 40, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-04-14", "text": "Finally, after so many years, I managed to play and finish Assassin's Creed. Quite repetitive gameplay yet very enjoyable. Reminds me of Mad Max. You basically keep doing same\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665over and over again, yet it's somehow addictive and rewarding. I haven't found all the \"collectibles\" yet I finished all \"side\" activities out of all memory banks. Took me 13h of total gameplay to finish the game. I can honestly recommend the game. Despite time passed since original release, it's still worth checking, for the gameplay and for quite interesting story. :)", "hours": 13.9, "username": "Impinfidel", "products": 1070, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 40, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-04-14", "text": "A classic that opens you to the Assassin's Creed series.", "hours": 27.3, "username": "swagmaster9000", "products": 145, "early_access": false}
