{"product_id": "15100", "page": 55, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-28", "text": "Hello guys I've just finished the game and would like to give a quick review! So lets start!\nStory: The story is a bit linear but the dialogs are sometimes very good!\nGameplay: One thing which completly made me crazy was the climbing/free-run in this game because sometimes it's just completly buggy (But it's an older game so I guess we have to accept it)\nGraphics: Are very good for it's time!\nAtmosphere: The cities are very crouded but there are not lot of options to interact with the people!\nFighting: The fighting-system is very good and sometimes also a bit challenging!\nSo to sum it up I would just recommend this for people who are real assasins-creed-fans and people who would like to now how the whole series starts but for that I think it would be enough to watch a 5min video on youtube!", "hours": 11.8, "user_id": "76561198064226839", "username": "J0hny Salam1", "products": 104, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
