{"product_id": "15100", "page": 56, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-27", "text": "I give it an 8/10.\nFirst in the series... Definitely should be the first one you play.\nMy biggest complaint about this game is that there are no rewards for getting the bonuses or killing templars.\nOther than that, really fun.\nBut so far, I think AC2 is my favorite, followed by AC: Brotherhood tied with AC: Revelations...\nEach one has better gameplay, but AC2 had unique puzzled temples which were intriguing to climb through.\nI am about to start on AC3 now.", "hours": 29.3, "username": "SchicagoS", "products": 253, "early_access": false}
