{"product_id": "15100", "page": 56, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-12-27", "text": "BEWARE PEOPLE! DO NOT BUY THIS GAME! I bought AC 1, 2 and Brotherhood during the Winter sales in 2016. I loved AC so much back in the day. This port is horrible, not the game. My xbox 360 controller did not end up working at first and I had to tweak around to get it to work, the tutorial kept freezing constantly and I could not get anywhere and it is so damn glitchy. It's honestly a glitch fest! I am refunding it!\nAltair was spinning in circles like a glitchy ball during the tutorial and I do not want to risk anything. It's $6.79 on sale but this should be $2-3 since it's been out for almost 10 years! I rather save my money and get something optimized!", "hours": 0.8, "username": "Kamuran", "products": 311, "early_access": false}
