{"product_id": "15100", "page": 58, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-23", "text": "The original game that launched a very successful series. Although Assassin's Creed Black Flag is my favorite among the series (to date), this game is still a good game that sets the stage for the entire series.\nPositives:\nGameplay was entertaining, good story line, optional methods to complete each mission, plenty of side missions, large area/map for the date of the game.\nNegatives:\nSide missions and map exploration can become repetative for completionists", "hours": 36.8, "user_id": "76561197972326029", "username": "WiseOldMan", "products": 113, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 58, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-23", "text": "Solid first game for a pretty decent franchise (except a couple of games). However the side missions get very repetitive after a while...", "hours": 37.7, "username": "Mustafa Keser", "products": 120, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
