{"product_id": "15100", "page": 62, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-27", "text": "Play the main story only... but then I think you have to complete town achievements...\nWorst part about town achievements is that there are a bazillion towns, and each one the achievements are a copy paste of what you have already done in the last 50 towns... so repetitive!", "hours": 27.8, "username": "KamikaziFly", "products": 416, "early_access": false}
