{"product_id": "15100", "page": 64, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-24", "text": "This is the one that started it all. Almost a decade old and the thing is still very much enjoyable to play. The graphics are still passable, but you can tell that they were made for a system much weaker than what we're used to today. There is a graphics mod on modDB that fixes this. Playing with a controller is highly recommended.\nStill my favourite of all the AC games.", "hours": 8.2, "username": "Halvtand", "products": 415, "early_access": false}
