{"product_id": "15100", "page": 77, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-23", "text": "You guys know that saying \"you never know what you have until it's gone\"? I don't think I'll ever love a man as much as I love Altair.", "hours": 23.7, "username": "Jettadura", "products": 135, "found_funny": 8, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 77, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-22", "text": "It's hard to deny: Assassin's Creed was a game changer. I was obsessed with this game when it came out, and having just replayed it recently, I can say that it's withstood the test of time rather well.\nFor those of you that prefer the controller to the keyboard,\nwas a big help for me.", "hours": 14.1, "username": "Flavvy", "products": 716, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
