{"product_id": "15100", "page": 78, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-15", "text": "Travel back in time.\nGet stabbed. Then demoted.\nRide to one of three dusty cities.\nClimb everything taller than you.\nInterrogate. Eavesdrop. Pickpocket. Kill. Repeat 8 more times.\nReturn home.\nDon't even TRY to understand the ending.\nGo back and pick fights with 50+ soldiers at once because you can.\n6/10\nP.S.\nGod hates flags.", "hours": 14.9, "user_id": "76561198038862056", "username": "robomac13", "products": 187, "found_funny": 17, "early_access": false}
