{"product_id": "15100", "page": 81, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-05-11", "text": "When I bought a new laptop with some power after some years, I thought I would catch up with some goodies from the past I couldn't play and went straight to this game.\nAt first it seemed fun but then turned out to be a series of boring, repetitive chores. Especially the travels between cities, similar missions to pickpocket some characters or going eagles' eye are not interesting after a while and definitely not fun.\nGet it if you have a lot of time to spend doing same actions and watching some good cut-scenes in between though.", "hours": 5.9, "username": "dmrknu", "products": 42, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
