{"product_id": "15100", "page": 96, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-15", "text": "If you haven't played the assassin's creed games I would not reccomend starting here!\nThe newer games play much better (although the story isn't as good as in this one)\nBasically any assassins creed game is an addition to this one in forms of movement, combat, quests, characters and story.\nYou play one... you really have played them all\nGreat game would reccomend if you love the other games\n9/10 - (when thew game was released)\n6/10 - (Compared to the newer games)", "hours": 2.4, "username": "Digit", "products": 446, "early_access": false}
