{"product_id": "15100", "page": 97, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-12-14", "text": "So ambitious! Tries to do alot and is a little exhausting at times but it's still an immense and beautiful game. The combat is more mechanical than the future games which I found actually enjoyable. You cannot slaughter a million men with ease, you really have to pick your fights and your kills.\nSet up an even greater game, Assassin's Creed II, so check it out if you get the chance.", "hours": 24.7, "username": "Mikemcn21", "products": 659, "early_access": false}
