{"product_id": "15100", "page": 100, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-25", "text": "Yes i know this game is old\nYes it is still fun\nReally enjoyed the story of this one it really gets you ready for the ridiculous amount of sequels this series has produiced and out of the ones i have played they are really\nPositives :\nReally fun story\nPrepares you for the second game which in my opinion is also really good\nassassinations are great\nAltair is a total badass\nNegatives :\nAfter the story is complete there is not much else to do\nmost of the assassination set ups are pretty much the same\nReally enjoyable campaign but not much after that 7/10", "hours": 13.9, "username": "Low Resolution Ayylien", "products": 30, "early_access": false}
