{"product_id": "15100", "page": 100, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-11-25", "text": "I had decided over the summer that I would start playing the AC games, so like usual I went to the first game, then I could at least get a feel for what the other games may be like. Though this game is very different from the other ones, I found it to be a fun start.\nIf you have ever played any of the other AC games, I recommend not playing this one. I thought it was a good starting game though for the franchise.", "hours": 35.2, "user_id": "76561198159693937", "username": "Starknight", "products": 4, "early_access": false}
