{"product_id": "15100", "page": 118, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-22", "text": "a great game!\ni've played on the nintendo ds, xbox 360 now on pc its looks amazing!\nthough when using keyboard/mouse i really had to pay attention to the begining tutorial to see what key/button is what xP (xbox controller might be usefull)\nwhen you first start up the game ubisoft may ask ya to register you don't have to.\nalso if you have the problem when you are not able to get into full screen just exit the game and restart assassin's creed.\nwhen i first installed the game it worked fine with windows 7 64bit hp\nbut after reinstalling i have to run in compatibility mode.", "hours": 4.9, "user_id": "76561198126126106", "username": "Knemi_Sempai", "products": 139, "early_access": false}
