{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-21", "text": "There are three words that can describe this game perfectly.\nMind-numbing tedium.\nEverything gets absurdly repetitive after the tutorial - \"climb towers, interrogate/pickpocket, run from guards, kill a guy, run some more\". The world and its characters are bland and uninspired, the combat is a chore, the controls are annoying and collecting clues is about as exciting as playing PacMan... without monsters.\nTo top it off, there are *no* subtitles, and considering that the characters talk like bumbling idiots more often than not, good luck understanding what's going on.\nJust... don't.", "hours": 10.4, "user_id": "76561198034238053", "username": "Justy", "products": 386, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-21", "text": "First Assassin's Creed game offers so much and requires so little\n10/10", "hours": 10.9, "username": "The CIA Guy", "products": 156, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "Great game, but poor controls and constant crashes make it virtually unplayable. Save yourself the pain; get it for Xbox.", "hours": 1.3, "user_id": "76561198072365126", "username": "Emberlynx", "products": 211, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "This game is a broken piece of\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665console port. All the time i spent in this game was trying to map my controls and trying to get passed all the bugs and glitches i cant even progress, I have a gtx 970, i5 4670K, 8 GBS ram, 1TB HDD. Do not Buy! Game is Broken!", "hours": 0.3, "user_id": "76561198110934463", "username": "skyblazer42", "products": 108, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "Unless you like being harrased by beggers, dealing with really crappy cameras,  questlines that have no instructions, and having to click 18 times just to get out of the game, avoid this title at all costs.", "hours": 6.0, "username": "Tkfore21", "products": 356, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "This game is just amazing!\nHistory, parkour, action, graphics, blood, combat,and it do acctually have an interesting story!\nThis is my second time I have brought this game. For some people it can seem old, but for me it brings back happy and epic memories :D\nI can remember the first time I climbed these enormous towers, killed my first templar!\nThis game brings so many memories and the Assassins creed series is just fantastic!\n&... their is No Uplay!\n10/10     \"Nothing is true, everything is permitted.\"", "hours": 20.2, "username": "HEY HEY MONIKA", "products": 148, "early_access": false}
