{"product_id": "15100", "page": 119, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-06-20", "text": "Bought on 75% summer sale, purely so i could play through the game that started the franchise.\nSadly, It keeps crashing every 10 minutes or so...\nWill try find a patch or fix (if one exists) then write an actual review.\nI'm guessing it has issues with newer PC builds.\nUpdate: Read the comment from Strazdaz, it fixed it for me. Thanks Strazdas! :)\nMy rig specs are:\ni7 4790K\n16GB DDR3\nGTX480\nWin764", "hours": 0.8, "user_id": "76561197970737738", "username": "Dr. Scheeses", "products": 464, "early_access": false}
