{"product_id": "15100", "page": 129, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-28", "text": "This is the first one of the AC series, it's a milestone though it has many drawbacks. Main flaw is that the storyline is too boring, you need to kill 8 people, namely 8 missions. However, each mission is almost the same, u need to pickpocket, you need to interrogation, bla bla.  But this is forgivable given that this is the first one and launched long time ago. I bought this coz this is a starter of a new era.", "hours": 18.8, "username": "Dr. \u041b\u0435\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0440\u0434\u0431\u043e\u043d\u0434\u0430\u0440\u044cAku Cinta Kamu", "products": 117, "early_access": false}
