{"product_id": "15100", "page": 144, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-24", "text": "One of the most boring repetitive games I have ever played... as a big fan of the Hitman series I was really looking forward to a good assassin game however this is more of a invincible swordsman simulator than a assassin game, you can literly take on a whole legion by yourself and win, every single assassination is the same as the other and every single side mission is the same as the other... even on sale I'm sorry I got this game :/", "hours": 10.3, "user_id": "76561198159474702", "username": "_bartul_", "products": 50, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 144, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-24", "text": "Good game with a good story.", "hours": 38.1, "user_id": "76561197972209171", "username": "zesaint", "products": 63, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 144, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-23", "text": "Recently Bought this game and the next three AC games off the Christmas Steam sale, and I'd say it was sincerely worth it. Now, this game might not seem cool at all if you've played the later Assassin's Creed games such as Black Flag, but if you're just starting, I highly recommend starting here, at ground zero. For me, the combat system was revolutionary, compared to Ubisoft's similar game series \"Prince of Persia,\" it was a major jump. The fact that the city environments in the game are completely open-ended are also an awesome addition. It helps add a realistic element and shows you the effort put into the virtual environment. Now, I personally loved following both story lines, but that may or may not be interesting at all to you. In the event that it isn't, there's plenty of gory combat and backstabbing to cure the itch. So, do I recommend this game, YES. Though it doesn't have a very high replay value, its got great combat and plus, it's the only Assassin's Creed game that saves you having to get Uplay, which can be a little difficult.", "hours": 76.6, "user_id": "76561198008155152", "username": "Dr. VonDerButch", "products": 19, "early_access": false}
