{"product_id": "15100", "page": 147, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-04", "text": "The \"partial controller support\" steam icon is total BS. This game was not properly ported for console control support. I tried playing it on a console control, and it was unplayable like that.", "hours": 0.5, "username": "Manberry Sauce", "products": 1486, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 147, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-04", "text": "Good game hidden under a story that, if you think about it, negates the whole game.\nAweful menu system that has you having to negotiate about 8 screens just to exit the game...including the need to exit to the spash screen and then load a game in order to exit. Madness!\nGame can get repetitive, but is so much fun...so who cares! Make me do the fun thing 100 more times.", "hours": 39.2, "username": "-|WaD|- BigMike\u2122", "products": 141, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 147, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-12-04", "text": "Assassin's Creed\nYou play as an Assassin, stealth or direct attack is your choice!\n+ Great theme\n+ Awesome graphic for old game\n+ Great story\n- Parkour control is like a crap\n- No swim allowed\n- Repetitive mission", "hours": 13.2, "username": "Talos", "products": 51, "early_access": false}
