{"product_id": "15100", "page": 148, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-12-03", "text": "I really want to recommend this game but the lack of subtitles makes the story very difficult to follow for the hearing impaired. I really have terrible hearing and my wife is half deaf so neither of us can enjoy a story driven title without subtitle options available.", "hours": 29.2, "user_id": "76561198012719580", "username": "Mega Man", "products": 210, "early_access": false}
