{"product_id": "15100", "page": 150, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-26", "text": "First of the best series of assassin games every wityh free running, stragey, and execution this game is a snich to that . Delivering stunning visauls and story plot really well developed game that has hit the hearts and throats of the gamers how have stepped into the shoes of this famous assassian of history of video games . This title is very deservent of it playability and how the game flows take heart patince and timing will deliver all the action you will want in this game so comn and enjoy the Assassin's Creed!!!!!!!", "hours": 17.7, "username": "Fr33 ( Playing EFT)", "products": 1300, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 150, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-11-24", "text": "This is the first Assassin's Creed game, which brought about a very innovative assassination gameplay system, balanced amounts of collectibles, a pretty entertaining storyline, and a very rich Levant world.\nThen again, this is also the progenitor of the Assassin's Creed money-grabbing franchise monolith.", "hours": 20.5, "username": "CaffeineMachine", "products": 578, "early_access": false}
