{"product_id": "15100", "page": 152, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-17", "text": "Assassin's Creed is a cool game, no doubt.\nIt's just that it might delete your saves! That happened to me two times! After the second time I didn't want to do it all again. After the first time I thought I'd give the game another try but it disappointed me.\nI really would have liked to complete the game however it's not possible without starting again and again.\nMoreover, it's quite frustrating to have to start again and so I don't recommend buying this game.\nIt is fun, it is cool but it's not possible to complete the game without becoming frustrated.", "hours": 11.5, "username": "Th4tsiT", "products": 197, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
