{"product_id": "15100", "page": 160, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-15", "text": "First Assassin's creed.\nI liked running around and the stealth portions however I have to say that sitting down in some areas and having to listen in on conversations is not so fun. The main character has an out of place accent, and the portions in which you must play as a character beyond Altair get boring.\nGame has problems with pacing, but overall I'd recommend this game. It's interesting and I enjoyed it.", "hours": 18.1, "username": "Solo \u30b7", "products": 343, "early_access": false}
