{"product_id": "15100", "page": 163, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-05", "text": "The 1st Series of The Assassin's Creed Game.\nThe game is good, you got to be an assassin that have to kill some target. The gameplay gives you freedom to kill the target. Whether you want to silence or having brawl fight.\nThe graphic is actually very good for a game released in 2009.\nI really recommended this game for all of you who like stealth game, action game, and open world game.", "hours": 26.3, "username": "Venterivia", "products": 446, "early_access": false}
