{"product_id": "15100", "page": 176, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-29", "text": "A little repative and a little wonky as far as controls go (xbox controller), but the ending made the game worth playing. Some of the flaws are expected since it was a port from console and the game was made in 2008.", "hours": 12.1, "username": "dzinction", "products": 360, "early_access": false}
