{"product_id": "15100", "page": 187, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-03-23", "text": "Assassin's creed is a wonderful adventure game. The enviroment in this game is very realistic and pretty. The game story is very intresting that you sometimes don't want to quit the game. I also like the gameplay itself that you can climp up buildings and jump from roof to roof. The combats are a bit difficult in the beginning but you will lern pretty quickly how to do. I hope when I buy AC 2 that it is even better than the first one.", "hours": 29.4, "user_id": "76561198091512912", "username": "xxXBatBoyXxx", "products": 235, "early_access": false}
