{"product_id": "15100", "page": 201, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-01-09", "text": "It spawned a huge number of sequels that made a lot of improvements, but the first one in the series I found to be really boring and stopped plaaying after a few hours.", "hours": 16.2, "username": "Horselord", "products": 190, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
