{"product_id": "15100", "page": 219, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-06-08", "text": "The first step into next gen.-games.\nThis game is not the best in the series,but is the place where all it start.", "hours": 3.3, "username": "ancient200", "products": 1673, "early_access": false}
