{"product_id": "15100", "page": 219, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-30", "text": "Assassins Creed 1... You should play this if you like assassins creed.\nThis game is also really repedetive and get boring but it worth it :D\ni think..                         6.5/10", "hours": 71.2, "username": "DavveBoii", "products": 149, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 219, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-26", "text": "A truly revolutionay game. The locales are vast, exotic, and intriguing. The game does an excellent job of sticking to it's goal: assassinations, but on the side note it is rediculously fun to run around on rooftops and climb towers, churches, mosques, castles, EVERYTHING. It's almost more fun to climb around than actually assassinate the targets. On the negative side, the missions involving finding information about your target are rather redundant and there is no real reward (besides a save point) to spending time looking for all those flags. Also the game requires a powerful machine if played on PC due to it's hardcore spec requirements. Otherwise, a masterful, enchanting, and must-play game", "hours": 23.4, "user_id": "76561198054801926", "username": "Malrogg", "products": 123, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 219, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-25", "text": "\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430 \u0441 \u0440\u0435\u0432\u043e\u043b\u044e\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u043d\u044b\u043c \u0433\u0435\u0439\u043c\u043f\u043b\u0435\u0435\u043c \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0435\u0433\u043e \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0438, \u043d\u043e \u043f\u043b\u043e\u0445\u043e\u0439 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0435\u0439.", "hours": 19.0, "username": "Jaime Cobb", "products": 208, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 220, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-05-23", "text": "A pesar de ser un juego antiguo este juego es necesario para entender la historia de Assassin\"s Creed  , ya que cuenta la historia de altair y del porque inicio todo esto . Su jugabilidad no es de las mejores pero una vez que te acostumbras no es tan malo , en fin .\nNota: 60", "hours": 22.4, "user_id": "76561198035562095", "username": "Tino", "products": 206, "early_access": false}
