{"product_id": "15100", "page": 223, "page_order": 4, "recommended": false, "date": "2013-02-24", "text": "O 1\u00ba jogo da famosa s\u00e9rie Assassin's Creed. O mais dificil, mas tamb\u00e9m bastante repetitivo tanto no seu conte\u00fado como tamb\u00e9m no combate. T\u00eam um ambiente e recria\u00e7\u00e3o de Jerus\u00e1lem na 3\u00aa Cruzada expecionais. A sua sequela (AC2) \u00e9 uma melhora\u00e7\u00e3o deste em todos aspectos.", "hours": 2.9, "username": "Ho Ho Hoes! Merry Xmas!", "products": 46, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "15100", "page": 223, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-02-19", "text": "Assassin's Creed can be vaguely compared to the concept of 'The Matrix' in which you play a protagonist in the 'real world' who becomes someone else inside a 'virtual world'. It tells a fictional story of a war between Assassins and Templars - and spans across several real life historic periods. The franchise is one of few - which tells a massive story back-to-back instead of switching main characters half way through or making massive time jumps. Awesome franchise!", "hours": 0.0, "username": "Vendrium", "products": 819, "early_access": false}
