{"product_id": "15100", "page": 224, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-01-30", "text": "--------------------------------------------------  8/10  -------------------------------------------------\nESPA\u00d1OL: Para quien no lo haya jugado a\u00fan; Este juego es muy interesante, buenos graficos, una historia muy bien planteada, con muchos matices religiosos y filosoficos pero que no se torna aburrida, buen balance y una jugabilidad con muy pocos fallos. Esta version Director's Cut (Steam) solo difiere de la original en que cada asesinato tiene una mision m\u00e1s. TIEMPO APROXIMADO PARA COMPLETAR: 12 Horas sin realizar misiones extra.\nENGLISH: If you havent played it yet: This is a really interesting game, nice graphics, a well planned story, with religious and philosophical shades of meaning but it doesnt become boring, good balance and a gameplay with very few errors. The difference between  this Director's Cut version (Steam) and the original one is an extra mission for each murder. ESTIMATED TIME TO COMPLETE: 12 Hours without extra missions.", "hours": 23.4, "username": "Tomsthreem", "products": 325, "early_access": false}
