{"product_id": "15100", "page": 226, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-12-16", "text": "While the more recent installments have, at least in my opinion, begun to stray a bit from the path of quality over to the path of quantity, I still believe that the Assassin's Creed Series, every single one of them, is worth every penny and a must-have for anyone who likes action games mixed with stealth and an awesome story. 9/10", "hours": 40.2, "username": "Mad Iorveth", "products": 149, "early_access": false}
