{"product_id": "15100", "page": 228, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-11-22", "text": "The Assassin's Creed series is a fun one, I'm glad I picked this game up!\nGreat for anyone who wants to release some stress by being an acrobatic assassin, and wants an AWESOME story to go along with it!", "hours": 30.6, "username": "Rrina", "products": 157, "early_access": false}
