{"product_id": "15100", "page": 233, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-07-22", "text": "You play as you playing a video game called assassin\u2019s Creed then play as guy called desmond who plays a character inside a computer called altair to find out this there is apple of Eden thing-a-ma-gig which controls other people living in computers.\nThe whole things got more plot twist than an episode of LOST so you might as well just run around punching lepers in the face like I did. And looking the ending on Wikipedia.", "hours": 1.3, "username": "Luke Rising", "products": 391, "early_access": false}
