{"product_id": "15100", "page": 243, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2011-12-27", "text": "Good story, but the game play is so repetiously boring that I am having trouble completing the game.", "hours": 4.1, "username": "ER|Banned", "products": 331, "early_access": false}
