{"product_id": "15100", "page": 248, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2011-07-05", "text": "Solid sword fighting mechanic, intriguing storyline, and long gameplay time (> 14 hours).  What more can you want?", "hours": 16.5, "username": "Gh0styy", "products": 102, "early_access": false}
